text: A neighborhood shopping center with a interesting mix of coffee shop, restaurant, flower shop and other eateries.
We can buy many things here. Got Heartland Mall, Kings burger ,NTUC, Kovan market Kopitiam,Bakery ,beauty spa n others. Easy to reach this place because near MRT n bust stop.

McDonalds is located there & a busy one too for breakfast. Very long queue of numbers but it clears quite fast.
Busy place for a Sunday as the wet market is next to it. Great place to shop for everything food wise especially.

Small busy area, people gather for meetup and shopping. Mostly, has CK, pet shops, key makers, hardware shops, few food courts, connected with wet market/hawker centre & mall at the end. There is a small open area, kid play area. The old large open space and car park are gone now.

Quite an old Hdb estate centre, with bus interchange and mrt for easy connectivity. Has lots of shops and malls, with a huge food centre. We bought some stuff at Fairprice Finest, which is at one end of the centre.
